{"tid":1577621,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇機會眾籌電視尋人？","createTime":"2019-09-17T19:23:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T02:00:38.000Z","uid":39526,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3ee5b03c818719baf4d33def199ba6bf4a0f6c82","tid":1577621,"uid":39526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T19:23:17.000Z","msg":"事到如今 <br />\n懷疑失蹤或者真係失蹤既人數已經好多<br />\n其實恐怖唔在於有人失蹤<br />\n恐怖在於無論真假 <br />\n冇真係識當事人既人出黎澄清<br />\n要真正滅口難道之高 大家唔難想像<br />\n朋友 家人 親戚 同事 唔見左個人實有人知<br />\n所以極大機會係相關人事都未必知我地搵緊人<br />\n<br />\n所以要開始做野<br />\n用接觸到更多人既方式尋人<br />\n尋找真相<br />\n<br />\n可以係電台 電視 街招等等<br />\n<br />\n集思廣益"},{"pid":"f4e4a8da8aeddb8aa2051467479667099789f4d3","tid":1577621,"uid":39526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T19:24:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ebbca8912051b6750b740c684d53b0b52f2b779c","tid":1577621,"uid":39526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T19:24:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1b3cfb62d9532e6e14dad0566853188548f732c4","tid":1577621,"uid":39526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T19:24:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ec820cbbda4461c4986376ac9f7c47163790636","tid":1577621,"uid":39526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T19:25:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b7f97d993809f172e888e3e00c2fd4e37f678e96","tid":1577621,"uid":39526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T19:25:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a52870625848b3c2ee3ef998d061b98c36a36fed","tid":1577621,"uid":91041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T19:25:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"12b744738b58331ed55d1a019230363dce41d4c5","tid":1577621,"uid":39526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T19:26:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ea289ace654cbae838075874736d1ad94879798","tid":1577621,"uid":39526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T19:26:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"11